<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.7.5">
<l>toṇṭaru mamararum muṉivarum toḻuteḻa</l>
<l>vaṇṭamo ṭakaliṭa maḷantava ramarcceytu</l>
<l>viṇṭavar paṭamati ḷilaṅkaimuṉ ṉeriyeḻa</l>
<l>kaṇṭavar kaṇapura maṭikaḷta miṭamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of god, the one who measured the broad land and the universe,</l>
<l>As devotees, immortals, and sages rose worshipping,</l>
<l>Of the one who once watched as flames rose in walled Laṅkā,</l>
<l>Having made war so that his rivals died, is Kaṇṇapuram.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
